======================================================================
PROVED FORMULAS
======================================================================

  Omega_0/p = 1
  Omega_1/p = m
  Omega_2/p = m(m-1)                     [rank(C_2) = m]
  Omega_3/p = m(m-1)(2m-3)/2             [rank(C_3) = 2m(m-1)]
  nullity(C_4) = m²                       [tensor product coupling]

  UNIVERSAL RATIOS:
    rank(C_2)/|A_2| = 1/m
    rank(C_3)/|A_3| = 4/p

  BETTI (HYP-672, verified P_7 and P_11):
    β_0 = 1, β_m = m(m-3)/2, β_{m+1} = C(m+1,2)
    β_d = 0 for d ∉ {0, m, m+1}
    chi = p

